Uses of Class
org.cougaar.core.qos.profile.ProfilerBase

Packages that use ProfilerBase
org.cougaar.core.qos.profile Utility components to periodically log performance metrics, such as the cpu load and message traffic. 
 

Uses of ProfilerBase in org.cougaar.core.qos.profile
 

Subclasses of ProfilerBase in org.cougaar.core.qos.profile
 class BlackboardSize
          This component profiles the per-agent blackboard size and add/change/remove counts for standard blackboard object types (UniqueObject, Task, etc).
 class JavaHeapSize
          This component profiles the JVM heap size (used, free, total, max).
 class Load
          This component profiles the MetricsService's load metrics for the cpu, messaging, and persistence load of the node aggegate, each agent, and core services (mts & metrics).
 class LocalTraffic
          This component profiles the message traffic (message count and byte count) of each local agents to any target.
 class NodeTraffic
          This component profiles the aggregate message traffic of all local agents to any target.
 class PersistSize
          This component profiles persistence activity for each agent and the aggegate node "sum".
 class ProcLoadAvg
          This component profiles the CPU load from "/proc/loadavg".
 class ProcMemInfo
          This component profiles system memory usage from "/proc/meminfo".
 class ProcNetDev
          This component profiles system network activity from "/proc/net/dev".
 class ProcStat
          This component profiles system activity from "/proc/stat".
 class ProcStatus
          This component profiles the JVM's process size from "/proc/self/status" (VmSize & VmRSS).
 class RemoteTraffic
          This component profiles the message traffic (message count and byte count) from the local aggregated agents to each specific remote target agent.
 class Resources
          This component profiles the MetricsService's summary resource metrics (load average, tcp use, etc).
 class Throughput
          This component profiles the aggregate "messages per second" throughput for all agents on the local node.
 class TrafficMatrix
          This component profiles the agent traffic matrix for all local-to-local and local-to-remote agent messaging.
 class VmStat
          This component profiles the output of the "/usr/bin/vmstat" command, which summarizes the system performance.
